Steam has launched its Summer Sale, offering great deals on thousands of PC games from 24 June to 8 July. The PC gaming platform has slashed the prices of several popular titles to under R100, ranging from big-name AAA games by major to studios, to independent titles from smaller developers. This year’s McGuffin for the sale is “Forge Your Fate”, which lets players choose from two possible actions in fourteen stories found throughout the sale. As a reward for participating you receive an animated sticker as a memento of your decision. Upon completing all of the stories, you’ll get one of five unique badges reflecting your choices. We have scoured the sale to find the best value for money deals. Below are the 15 best games for under R100 we found across Steam’s 2021 Summer Sale: <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-403455" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/titanfall-2-cover-640x427.jpg" alt="titanfall 2 cover" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/titanfall-2-cover-640x427.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/titanfall-2-cover-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/titanfall-2-cover.jpg 701w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-403467" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/wolfenstein-2-the-new-colossus-cover-640x427.jpg" alt="wolfenstein-2-the-new-colossus-cover" width="640" height="427" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/wolfenstein-2-the-new-colossus-cover-640x427.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/wolfenstein-2-the-new-colossus-cover-600x400.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/wolfenstein-2-the-new-colossus-cover.jpg 701w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 